 \"score\": 0.9999999998376552, \"rank\": 9.402522089430233e-11, \"text\": \"Ukraine\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their approach\", \"from\": 5231, \"to\": 5245}, {\"ngram\": \"sanctions\", \"from\": 5257, \"to\": 5266}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With the Russian leadership of the IBA, this position highlights another layer ofgeopolitical complexity in this case.\", \"from\": 5310, \"to\": 5428, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5319, \"end\": 5326, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"score\": 0.991366210055942, \"rank\": 0.008707604119343978, \"text\": \"Russian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\"}, {\"begin\": 5345, \"end\": 5348, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.569798696966731, \"rank\": 0.7550057683941591, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\", \"Q141683\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel_Broadcasting_Authority\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this position\", \"from\": 5350, \"to\": 5363}, {\"ngram\": \"another layer ofgeopolitical complexity\", \"from\": 5375, \"to\": 5414}, {\"ngram\": \"this case\", \"from\": 5418, \"to\": 5427}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Responding to the media frenzy after the Khelif-Carini bout, the Paris 2024 boxing unit stated: \\\"all athletes participating in the boxing tournament comply with the competition's eligibility and entry regulations, as well as all applicable medical regulations set by the Paris 2024 Boxing Unit (PBU)\\\".\", \"from\": 5430, \"to\": 5731, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5495, \"end\": 5505, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.49131118422137e-21, \"