5}, {\"ngram\": \"a payment\", \"from\": 5786, \"to\": 5795}, {\"ngram\": \"the purse\", \"from\": 5807, \"to\": 5816}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic champion\", \"from\": 5828, \"to\": 5848}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Since the incident, Carini hasapologised to Kheliffor her reaction and the resulting abuse, stating she would \\\"embrace her\\\" the next time they meet.\", \"from\": 5864, \"to\": 6012, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5884, \"end\": 5890, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"score\": 0.999995342366152, \"rank\": 4.657655530723754e-06, \"text\": \"Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the incident\", \"from\": 5870, \"to\": 5882}, {\"ngram\": \"Kheliffor\", \"from\": 5908, \"to\": 5917}, {\"ngram\": \"her reaction\", \"from\": 5918, \"to\": 5930}, {\"ngram\": \"the resulting abuse\", \"from\": 5935, \"to\": 5954}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the contemporary context, many sportswomen who appear too powerful, too successful, or look \\\"too masculine\\\" according to a particular set of values are at risk of being targeted.\", \"from\": 6014, \"to\": 6195, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the contemporary context\", \"from\": 6017, \"to\": 6041}, {\"ngram\": \"many sportswomen\", \"from\": 6043, \"to\": 6059}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"too masculine\", \"from\": 6109, \"to\": 6123}, {\"ngram\": \"a particular set\", \"from\": 6138, \"to\": 6154}, {\"ngram\": \"values\", \"from\": 6158, \"to\": 6164}, {\"ngram\": \"risk\", \"from\": 6172, \"to\": 6176}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Importantly, it is most oftennon-white athleteswho face the most scrutiny of their gendered sporting bodies.\", \"from\": 6196, \"to\": 6304, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"most oftennon-white athleteswho\", \"from\": 6215, \"to\": 6246}, {\"ngram\": \"the most scrutiny\", \"from\": 6252, \"to\": 6269}, {\"ngram\": \"their gendered sporting bodies\", \"from\": 6273, \"to\": 6303}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Beyond the ethics of the tests being used, the extreme levels ofonline abusedirected to sportswomen such as Khelif and Lin reveal new ways in which women's bodies are being policed and regulated.\", \"from\": 6306, \"to\": 6501, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the ethics\", \"from\": 6313, \"to\": 6323}, {\"ngram\": \"the tests\", \"from\": 6327, \"to\": 6336}, {\"ngram\": \"the extreme levels\", \"from\": 6349, \"to\": 6367}, {\"ngram\": \"sportswomen\", \"from\": 6394, \"to\": 6405}, {\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 6414, \"to\": 6420}, {\"ngram\": \"Lin\", \"from\": 6425, \"to\": 6428}, {\"ngram\": \"new ways\", \"from\": 6436, \"to\": 6444}, {\"ngram\": \"women's bodies\", \"from\": 6454, \"to\": 6468}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To avoid such accusations, many sportswomen are engaging in what scholars have termed \\\"emphasised femininity\\\" - wearing long lashes, jewellery, make-up, painted nails and overtly feminine clothing.\", \"from\": 6503, \"to\": 6700, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6636, \"end\": 6645, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jewellery\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.622672958914701e-16, \"text\": \"jewellery\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jewellery\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jewellery\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"such accusations\", \"from\": 6512, \"to\": 6528}, {\"ngram\": \"many sportswomen\", \"from\": 6530, \"to\": 6546}, {\"ngram\": \"scholars\", \"from\": 6568, \"to\": 6576}, {\"ngram\": \"femininity\", \"from\": 6601, \"to\": 6611}, {\"ngram\": \"long lashes\", \"from\": 6623, \"to\": 6634}, {\"ngram\": \"make-up\", \"from\": 6647, \"to\": 6654}, {\"ngram\": \"painted nails\", \"from\": 6656, \"to\": 6669}, {\"ngram\": \"overtly feminine clothing\", \"from\": 6674, \"to\": 6699}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is not because it enhances their performance but toreassure audiences(and critics) of their femininity.\", \"from\": 6701, \"to\": 6809, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their performance\", \"from\": 6733, \"to\": 6750}, {\"ngram\": \"critics\", \"from\": 6780, \"to\": 6787}, {\"ngram\": \"their femininity\", \"from\": 6792, \"to\": 6808}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If they do not offer a convincing performance that meets limited versions of femininity, they may also face surveillance of their gendered bodies, and public attack and online abuse.\", \"from\": 6811, \"to\": 6993, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a convincing performance\", \"from\": 6832, \"to\": 6856}, {\"ngram\": \"limited versions\", \"from\": 6868, \"to\": 6884}, {\"ngram\": \"femininity\", \"from\": 6888, \"to\": 6898}, {\"ngram\": \"surveillance\", \"from\": 6919, \"to\": 6931}, {\"ngram\": \"their gendered bodies\", \"from\": 6935, \"to\": 6956}, {\"ngram\": \"public attack\", \"from\": 6962, \"to\": 6975}, {\"ngram\": \"online abuse\", \"from\": 6980, \"to\": 6992}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, this recent controversy may be a distraction from the real issues affecting women's sport, such as safeguarding against systematic abuse, which has been seen in recent high-profile cases involvingVolleyball Australiaand USA Gymnastics.\", \"from\": 6995, \"to\": 7239, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7224, \"end\": 7238, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Gymnastics\", \"score\": 0.9999999987139745, \"rank\": 1.2862075330126309e-09, \"text\": \"USA Gymnastics\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Gymnastics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Gymnastics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this recent controversy\", \"from\": 7004, \"to\": 7027}, {\"ngram\": \"a distraction\", \"from\": 7035, \"to\": 7048}, {\"ngram\": \"the real issues\", \"from\": 7054, \"to\": 7069}, {\"ngram\": \"women's sport\", \"from\": 7080, \"to\": 7093}, {\"ngram\": \"systematic abuse\", \"from\": 7124, \"to\": 7140}, {\"ngram\": \"recent high-profile cases\", \"from\": 7165, \"to\": 7190}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While the Paris Olympic and Paralympics may be celebrated as the first\\\"gender equitable\\\" games, with 50% female participation, the abuse faced by Khelif and Yu-Ting highlight the challenges many women still face in sport.\", \"from\": 7241, \"to\": 7462, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7251, \"end\": 7256, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999998887001373, \"rank\": 1.1129993313756197e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Paralympics\", \"from\": 7269, \"to\": 7280}, {\"ngram\": \"the first\\\"gender equitable\\\" games\", \"from\": 7302, \"to\": 7335}, {\"ngram\": \"50% female participation\", \"from\": 7342, \"to\": 7366}, {\"ngram\": \"the abuse\", \"from\": 7368, \"to\": 7377}, {\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 7387, \"to\": 7393}, {\"ngram\": \"Yu-Ting\", \"from\": 7398, \"to\": 7405}, {\"ngram\": \"the challenges\", \"from\": 7416, \"to\": 7430}, {\"ngram\": \"many women\", \"from\": 7431, \"to\": 7441}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 7456, \"to\": 7461}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Copyright \\u00a9 2010-2026,The Conversation Media Group Ltd\", \"from\": 7464, \"to\": 7518, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Copyright \\u00a9 2010-2026,The Conversation Media Group Ltd\", \"from\": 7464, \"to\": 7518}]}]}"